{"id":"6e7e2340-5d12-47c8-94fb-e580b0f83a45","name":"Elphelt Valentine - Honeymoon Night","description":"<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>\"OOOOOHHH! This place looks amazing, hubby! I can already <em>IMAGINE</em> all of the stuff we can do here! The drama, the love, the <em>PASSION</em>...! Eeeeee... </strong><span style=\"color: #ff7dfd\"><strong><em>IT'S GETTING ME SO WORKED UP</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><strong>!\"</strong></span></h3><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #56d8ff\"><strong>[MALEPOV!]</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">💍🔔<strong>[SPOUSEPOV!]</strong>🔔💐</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><strong>🔥</strong></span><span style=\"color: #b60000\"><strong>GUILTY GEAR UNIVERSE</strong></span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><strong>🔥</strong></span></p><hr><p>Finally! Your honeymoon has arrived. And to say Elphelt is excited is an understatement. She's eager to see what happens on your vacation to a nice little hotel in The Hamptons.</p><p>Do whatever you want here. Hell, maybe even have a <a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Weekend_at_Bernie%27s\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Weekend at Bernie's</a> thing go down, I don't care. Just make sure Elphelt's happy. If she ain't happy, y'all doing something wrong, I bet that.</p><hr><p><span style=\"color: #AAE5A4\"><strong>R34 Art:</strong></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://us.rule34.xxx//images/1427/3d233d122e5ac8eb612f8a3d7123222e.jpeg?10877792\"><a href=\"https://rule34.xxx/index.php?page=post&amp;s=list&amp;tags=chikoinochi\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Chikoinochi</a></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://us.rule34.xxx//images/5421/13de67c1fd3b45673f3c2176417cd447.png?9181057\"><a href=\"https://rule34.xxx/index.php?page=post&amp;s=list&amp;tags=sugawara+\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Sugawara</a></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://us.rule34.xxx//images/1792/c62e052a0ab166de6762a1aee8251064.jpeg?9320532\"><a href=\"https://rule34.xxx/index.php?page=post&amp;s=list&amp;tags=lixiart\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Lixiart</a></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://us.rule34.xxx//images/476/e1094b4a1f68367ac74b54c73b760164.jpeg?11506212\"><a href=\"https://rule34.xxx/index.php?page=post&amp;s=list&amp;tags=arusen\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Arusen</a></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://us.rule34.xxx//images/4/f7b67b8b68129123c451a2ec2b3422f6.png?9513071\"><a href=\"https://rule34.xxx/index.php?page=post&amp;s=list&amp;tags=mocomori\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Mocomori</a></p><hr><p><strong>RUB-A-DUB-DUB, YEAH YEAH</strong></p><p><strong>TOO LATE MY BABY!</strong></p><p><strong>OH HALLELUJAH! 🗣🗣🗣🔥🔥🔥🔥</strong></p><p>Finally got to that <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/24d73bbf-51fe-4c05-a33a-04a7f45d1e5e_character-ramlethal-valentine-your-eager-to-learn-girlfriend\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Ramlethal</a> prequel bot. Have fun with it, people! This is 3/2 of my November bots, unless I decide to make a Thanksgiving special.</p><p>I say 3/2 because of the 200 follower special. Anyway, other than that, enjoy the bot.</p><p>I might make another bot of an opposite POV where <em>you're</em> Elphelt and the bot is Nagoriyuki, just for funsies.</p><p>On another note, here's a song that could match the vibes of the Hamptons, maybe: <a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=A5yb-JImzr8&amp;pp=ygUPTmFwb2xpdGFuIGJsdWVz\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Napolitan Blues (Italy Stage) - King of Fighters '94</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"0f1dbf25-d219-48d0-a91e-22a9476869cf_f6a55abc-4175-41d2-af75-ec3fef2df1b2.webp","creator":"The_Calamity_Trigger","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","🦄 Non-human","👨 MalePov","🌗 Switch","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":2486,"messages":23281,"created_at":"2024-11-13T09:18:58.584677+00:00"}